---
title: Hoisin-Sesame Chickpea Bowls with Green Onion Rice
description: Here's a veggie meal that packs a serious flavour punch! This meal features protein-rich chickpeas, sweet bell pepper and broccoli coated in a bold, sweet-and-savoury sauce. Basmati rice speckled with green onions adds a bit of herbaceous flair to every bite! Better than takeout? We think so!
